digiKam 9.0.0 - Release date: 2026-03-xx

*****************************************************************************************************
NEW FEATURES:

Bundles component versions:

(*): Updated compared to previous digiKam release.

| Bundles       | Qt version | KDE version | OpenCV version | FFmpeg version | Heif version | ExifTool version | Exiv2 version |
|---------------|------------|-------------|----------------|----------------|--------------|------------------|---------------|
| Windows Qt5   | 5.15.17    | 5.116       | 4.11           | 7.1.1          | 1.20.2       | 13.45 (*)        | 0.28.5        |
| Windows Qt6   | 6.9.1      | 6.17.0      | 4.11           | 7.1.1          | 1.20.2       | 13.45 (*)        | 0.28.5        |
| AppImage Qt5  | 5.15.18 (*)| 5.116       | 4.12           | 7.1.2 (*)      | 1.20.2 (*)   | 13.45 (*)        | 0.28.7 (*)    |
| AppImage Qt6  | 6.10.1 (*) | 6.20.0 (*)  | 4.12           | 7.1.2 (*)      | 1.20.2 (*)   | 13.45 (*)        | 0.28.7 (*)    |
| macOS Qt5     | 5.15.18 (*)| 5.116       | 4.12           | 7.1.2 (*)      | 1.20.2 (*)   | 13.45 (*)        | 0.28.7 (*)    |
| macOS Qt6     | 6.10.0 (*) | 6.20.0 (*)  | 4.12           | 7.1.2 (*)      | 1.20.2 (*)   | 13.45 (*)        | 0.28.7 (*)    |

Raw Engine      : Internal Libraw has been updated to the latest upstream 20260104 which brings with
                  it a variety of bug fixes and performance improvements.
                  New Raw Camera: * Canon EOS R1, EOS R5 Mark II, EOS R5 C, EOS R6 Mark II, EOS R8, EOS R50, EOS R100, EOS Ra
                                  * Fujifilm X-T50, GFX 100S II, GFX100-II, X-T5, X-S20, X-H2, X-H2S
                                  * Hasselblad  CFV-50c, CFV-100c, X2D-100c
                                  * Leica Q3 43, D-Lux8, SL3, Q3, M11 Monochrom
                                  * Nikon (standard compression only): Z6-III, Z f, Z30, Z8
                                  * Olympus/OM System OM-1 Mark II, TG-7, OM-5
                                  * Panasonic GH7, S9, DC-G9 II, DC-ZS200D / ZS220D, DC-TZ200D / TZ202D / TZ220D, DC-S5-II, DC-GH6
                                  * Pentax KF, K III Monochrome
                                  * Sony ZV-E10M2, UMC-R10C, A9-III, ILX-LR1, A7C-II, A7CR, ILCE-6700,  ZV-1M2, ZV-E1, ILCE-7RM5 (A7R-V), ILME-FX30, A1
                                  * Multiple DJI and Skydio drones
                                  * Tested with multiple smartphones with DNG format recorded.

Video           : Internal QtAVPlayer has been updated to the latest upstream 20251210 which brings with
                  it a variety of bug fixes and performance improvements (Qt5 only).

General         : Add support of customizable date format to show everywhere in the program. Seconds can be displayed with the shot time-stamp, and more.
Color Labels    : Color label names are now customizable in the Labels tab from left sidebar by double clicking on text. Label strings size are limited to 32 characters.
Sort Items      : Add support of Album Icon-View sort items by Pick and Color Labels.
Sort Items      : Add support of Import Icon-View sort items by Pick and Color Labels.
Sort Items      : Add support of Album Icon-View sort items by Orientation.
Sort Items      : Add support of Album Icon-View sort items by GPS location.
Sort Items      : Add support of Album Icon-View sort items by File Format.
Sort Items      : Add support of Import Icon-View sort items by File Format.
Setup Collection: Add regular expression wildcard support for ignored directories settings.
Image Properties: Add new button to copy all properties as text in clipboard.
Image Properties: Add new button to open current item is file manager.
Image Properties: If no icon-view item selected, show current album statistics.
Grouped Items   : Show items from an open group highlighted for a better usability.
Grouped Items   : Usability improvements of the grouped icon-view items overlay.
Filter Items    : Split filters view into 3 separated tabs for better usabilty: Properties, Tags, and People.
Trash View      : load and save column states between sessions.
Preview         : Extend Image and Video preview toolbar overlay with Labels editor.
Preview         : Add context-menu to the video player.
Preview         : Add load progress indicator on the status bar (Icon-view and LightTable).
Preview         : Add trackpad gesture events support to zoom the contents, pan the canvas, and change to previous/next items.
Preview         : Add a magnifier glass tool to zoom and explore a small area of the preview canvas. Tool Size and zoom factor are customizable.
Preview         : Add under and over exposure indicators for the preview canvas.
Preview         : Railway over the canvas is displayed as an overlay when the scrollbar are visible.
Icon-View       : Clicking on GPS icon overlay open the Geolocation tab from the left sidebar.
Table-View      : Add customizable columns to show "Grouped" and "Versioned" properties.
Advanced Rename : New modifier "Date Format".
Template        : Add support to merge existing template entries assigned in items with a new template.
SlideShow       : Add new option to customize the color background instead pure black in case of images transparency usage.
Presentation    : Add new option to customize the color background instead pure black in case of images transparency usage.
File Copy       : Complete rewrite the GUI for a better usability.
File Transfer   : Complete rewrite the GUI for a better usability.
Web Site        : Huge update of the contents and design eg. screenshots, description, history, features, support, download, etc.

